        {
            "id": 6435787,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 凌雲邏輯(CRUS-US)大跌5.02%，報162.21美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>凌雲邏輯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRUS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRUS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRUS-US</a>)截至台北時間28日22:50股價下跌8.58美元，報162.21美元，跌幅5.02%，成交量160,335（股），盤中最高價169.75美元、最低價162.21美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.01%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.74%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.33%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-4.93%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>凌雲邏輯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRUS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRUS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRUS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.43%</li> <li>近 1 月：+19.11%</li> <li>近 3 月：+31.78%</li> <li>近 6 月：+28.59%</li> <li>今年以來：+44.13%</li></ul></section></main>",
